{
  "stem": "18665.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Later on, he claimed that he protected the Jews from extermination by acting the way he did.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But who knows?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So were you restricted within the ghetto at that point?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And what other people were in the ghetto of Hongkew with you?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Were there only Jewish immigrants?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We lived in a Chinese neighborhood, occupied by Chinese.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But eventually, all 20,000 status refugees were living in the ghetto, in the district.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The majority had lived there, even before the war, and the rest filled up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We also had a very strong Jewish life because members of a [NON-ENGLISH] from Poland came to Shanghai via Japan, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were on the way to the United States, but was stopped there because of the war.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then they were transported to Shanghai, to Hongkew.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they give a tremendous sense of Jewish life and Judaism to the district, to the Jews who lived there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were not in danger, in a sense, unless there were infractions.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "One example, for instance, I remember was we were standing on a street corner and just talking.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Friend of mine had a bicycle.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the rear end of his bicycle was partially in the, in the roadway.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "A Japanese lorry or a Japanese truck came by, hit his bicycle.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he made a big fuss.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "My friend made a big fuss.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The truck stopped.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The driver and his companion came out in uniform.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And of course, not a word of English.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he said he wants it repaired.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He said, OK.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Put your bike on the back of the truck, and come with us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We've never heard, seen him again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
